{"tid":2353762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭媽媽：守法市民毋須擔心法制不同　不會迫年輕人上大灣區","createTime":"2021-01-05T03:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T06:24:02.000Z","uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7918adea461ab042b82047380aa4ea2d8190244","tid":2353762,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"12名涉觸犯內地偷越邊境罪的港人，日前被深圳鹽田人民法院判處有期徒刑7個月至3年不等，但家屬未能旁聽審訊及探監，家屬委託律師盧思位、任全牛更被當局吊銷牌照。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前，有記者質疑上述情況如何說服港人內地有「陽光司法」，林鄭指，12人在香港干犯嚴重罪行，屬畏罪潛逃，由於案件仍在司法階段不評論。"},{"pid":"ebacb4133934f69d2c1aa2ef22c3cdd893de37e9","tid":2353762,"uid":119695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"答唔到=不便評論"},{"pid":"03b65f82ca5f100ca46b65c081b9eebcf4bcacaf","tid":2353762,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"外賣員銀包見「光時」遭截查 要求證外賣袋非盜竊得來<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2353551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2353551</a>"},{"pid":"91847c5c935e7468915f3751d6e9000839eceb4d","tid":2353762,"uid":129664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"監都判埋仲司法階段？而家講緊探監都唔得，關司法階段乜事啊？對大陸嚟講只係偷渡咋，罪行有幾嚴重啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73b9eeb4f571524b6dd9a708e692fd2d0e267b8","tid":2353762,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"守法定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府既守法=唔准反抗政府，唔准持相反意見"},{"pid":"646ad538168ef76766fc0944c8cff615dff55b14","tid":2353762,"uid":8170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"講完一大輪嘢話唔評論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/n